parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, making it challenging to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering assist light is illuminated
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
especially at low speeds
the power steering default message is displayed
and the AdvanceTrac system failure message is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, and the prolonged delay in recall repairs can cause undue stress and anxiety for vehicle owners.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
airbag failure
lack of airbag deployment in an accident
and delayed or unavailable recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The prolonged delay in obtaining parts for the Takata airbag recall can cause undue stress and anxiety for vehicle owners, and the failure of airbags can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Delayed or unavailable recall repairs
lack of parts availability
and failure to notify owners of recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering assist system can cause the vehicle to lose power steering, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle loses power steering
the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, slip, or hesitate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips
the vehicle hesitates or loses power
the transmission warning light is illuminated
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
the transmission fluid is black or dirty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift cable can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly
the shift cable detaches from the transmission
the gearshift position shows the vehicle is in park but it is not.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission control module can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to slipping, hesitation, or loss of motive power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission control module needs to be reprogrammed or updated
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle loses power.
